author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Wesfarmers Says Excluding Significant Items, HY NPAT Down 2.7% TO $1,535 Mln
text:
Feb 21 (Reuters) - Wesfarmers Ltd:
* ‍HY OPERATING REVENUE $35.9 BILLION, UP 2.8%​ * ‍INTERIM DIVIDEND $1.03 PER SHARE​ * EXCLUDING THESE SIGNIFICANT ITEMS, NPAT FOR HALF-YEAR DECREASED 2.7 PER CENT TO $1,535 MILLION.
* HY NET PROFIT FOR PERIOD ATTRIBUTABLE TO MEMBERS DOWN 86.6% TO $212 MILLION Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (bangalore.newsroom@thomsonreuters.com)
